[Sammatti is located in the province of Southern Finland and is part of the Uusimaa region. The municipality had a population of 1365 (31 Dec 2008) and covered a land area of 72.01 square km. The population density was 18.96 inhabitants per square km (49.1/square mile). It can be located in the map at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sammatti. - Mod.CP

